        <p class="text-[#5C0000] mb-4">The Barnt Green Cattery is ideally located in the Birmingham countryside, close to Bromsgrove and Redditch. Our rural retreat has complete privacy and security, and is well away from noisy city traffic.</p>
        <p class="text-[#5C0000] mb-4">The cattery is South facing, so in the winter months the bad weather is behind us and the summer sun brings warmth and brightness all day long to the front of the cattery, which overlooks a colourful garden and large pond.</p>
