        <p class="text-[#5C0000] mb-4">The centrally heated bedrooms, warm winter quarters and large exercise conservatory make it the ideal base to explore. Our cat hotel has a total of forty individual chalets all designed and built to the highest standards.</p>
        <p class="text-[#5C0000] mb-4">All our chalets are built to F.A.B standards to accommodate at least two cats. We have twelve extra large family units for up to four cats. Our largest chalet, called the Penthouse, can accommodate up to eight cats. All cats staying in any chalet must be from the same household.</p>
        <p class="text-[#5C0000]">The chalets are fully insulated and individually heated with thermostat control, so that even in very cold weather our guests are warm as toast. Beds and bedding are off the floor on low tables. A picture window overlooks the individual, outside covered runs which have climbing frames, platforms and shelving at different heights.</p>
